msgid "Reinforcement Menu:"
msgstr "Menú de refuerzos:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/buys_on_after_flag"
msgid "Units unlock permanently"
msgstr "Desbloqueo de unidades permanente"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/name"
msgid "Downfall"
msgstr "La caída"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/name_big"
msgid "Downfall"
msgstr "La caída"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/place"
msgid "Berlin, Germany"
msgstr "Berlín, Alemania"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/date"
msgid "April, 1945"
msgstr "Abril de 1945"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/mission_hq"
msgid "You must keep control of your field HQ at all times!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debes mantener el control de su cuartel general de campo en todo momento!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/mission_attack"
msgid "Drive the enemy back into the outskirts!"
msgstr "¡Haz retroceder al enemigo a las afueras!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/flag_capture_status"
msgid "Your soldiers secured %1%/7 Soviet positions!"
msgstr "¡Tus soldados aseguraron el %1%/7 de las posiciones soviéticas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/outro_start"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/outro_completed"
msgid "Mission accomplished! We have secured this sector, good job!"
msgstr "¡Misión cumplida! Hemos asegurado este sector, ¡buen trabajo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/outro_failed"
msgid "Mission failed! Surely, this means the end..."
msgstr "¡Misión fallida! Seguramente, esto significa el fin..."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/outro_failed_hq"
msgid ""
"The soviet offensive has proved way too powerful for the defences of Berlin. "
"At this rate, the war will be over in a matter of days."
msgstr ""
"La ofensiva soviética ha demostrado ser demasiado poderosa para las defensas "
"de Berlín. A este ritmo, la guerra terminará en cuestión de días."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/story"
msgid "The Last Stand, streets of Berlin.\n\nBriefing: This battle will not end in a draw. If we want to win this one, something special is required. Good luck!\n\nGoals:\n - Secure a stock of AT weapons.\n - Destroy as many soviet tanks as you can."
msgstr ""
"La última batalla,\n"
"calles de Berlín. Informe:#Esta batalla no terminará en un empate.\n"
"Si queremos ganarla,\n"
"se requiere algo especial. ¡Buena suerte!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Objetivos:\n"
" - Asegurar un stock de armas AT.\n"
" - Destruir todos los tanques soviéticos que se pueda."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/narrator_start0"
msgid ""
"Welcome to Berlin, Major! This is your field HQ, make sure keep it secure!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenido a Berlín, Mayor! Este es su cuartel general de campo, ¡asegúrese "
"de mantenerlo seguro!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/narrator_start1"
msgid ""
"Soldaten! The Bolsheviks have tightened their grip on our beloved capital. "
"They have to be stopped here, or we will face total collapse. They may have "
"the numbers, but nothing will deter our conviction to the Fatherland. Do not "
"despair, keep fighting until the final victory has been achieved!"
msgstr ""
"¡Soldaten! Los bolcheviques han reforzado su control sobre nuestra querida "
"capital. Hay que detenerlos aquí, o nos enfrentaremos a un colapso total. "
"Puede que tengan los números, pero nada disuadirá nuestra convicción de la "
"Patria. No desesperéis, ¡seguid luchando hasta conseguir la victoria final!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/narrator_start2"
msgid ""
"The Red Army is already moving in from the outskirts of the city. We have to "
"stop them right here!"
msgstr ""
"El Ejército Rojo ya está avanzando desde las afueras de la ciudad. ¡Tenemos "
"que detenerlos aquí mismo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/narrator_start3"
msgid ""
"Coordinate the defence. Secure enough AT weapons to stand a chance against "
"the Soviet tanks. Use the buildings to hide your men. You might even get "
"reinforcements."
msgstr ""
"Coordina la defensa. Asegura suficientes armas AT para tener una oportunidad "
"contra los tanques soviéticos. Utiliza los edificios para esconder a tus "
"hombres. Puede que incluso recibas refuerzos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Major! Soviets are close to our Field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Mayor! ¡Los soviéticos están cerca de nuestro cuartel general!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid ""
"Never surrender the command post, or it will be considered high treason!"
msgstr "¡Nunca entregues el puesto de mando, o se considerará alta traición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/hq_bonus"
msgid "Major! Now you can request an airstrike."
msgstr "¡Mayor! Ahora puede solicitar un ataque aéreo."
